sentences.english: The setup here is very similar to the parsing of the main document.
sentences.chinese: 這裏的設置與主文檔的語法分析十分相似。

sentences.english: One branch of western philosophy, Existentialism, is very similar to Buddhist ideas.
sentences.chinese: 而西方哲學的旁支，存在主義，同佛教十分相似。

sentences.english: Our facial structure bears some resemblance to that of an immature ape.
sentences.chinese: 我們的面部結構就與幼猿十分相似。

sentences.english: So in that sense it’s very similar.
sentences.chinese: 所以在某種層面上，我們所做的十分相似。

sentences.english: Several demodulation schemes for split phase coded PSK signals are described in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文敘述了幾種分相碼移相信號的解調方案。

sentences.english: The opposition between Jupiter and Saturn suggests difficulty in recognizing personal limitations.
sentences.chinese: 木星與土星之間的對分相暗示着認知個人極限的困難。

sentences.english: Really the kakapo has a very similar life history to that iconic extinct bird the Dodo.
sentences.chinese: 梟鸚與絕種的渡渡鳥的生命歷史十分相似。

sentences.english: These are very similar to seminar type sessions with minimal interaction.
sentences.chinese: 這與只有極少互動的研討會十分相似。

sentences.english: It is also way cooler-looking, thanks to the CenterTrack design, which makes it look a lot more like a traditional chain-and-cog drive.
sentences.chinese: 外觀設計也相當漂亮，與傳統的鏈齒傳動十分相似。

sentences.english: The new album (Lunatic Harness)is pretty simliar to Richard's.
sentences.chinese: 新專輯《瘋狂的盔甲》和理查德的十分相似。

sentences.english: He flogged paintings by his apprentices that looked very much like his own.
sentences.chinese: 他還兜售那些與自己的作品十分相似的，學徒的繪畫。

sentences.english: Fishing cats are so similar in size and weight to the Ocelot, we couldn't split them up.
sentences.chinese: 漁貓的體型和體重都和豹貓十分相似，我們很難分辨。

sentences.english: This is similar to the elegy complex of the intellectuals during the Six Dynasties.
sentences.chinese: 這與六朝文士對於生死大化的輓歌情結十分相似。

sentences.english: The few translations of this inscription from Tortuguero Monument 6 are all very similar.
sentences.chinese: 本託土蓋羅紀念碑6題詞的幾個翻譯都十分相似。
